# The distributed Strategy Factory (factory/sync.py) commits per-machine
# shards and generated artifacts to the shared factory-pool branch and syncs
# them across machines. Pin those paths to LF so a pool that mixes Windows
# and macOS / Linux nodes does not churn line endings — otherwise a pulled
# file can show up as modified and trip sync_pull's dirty-tree check.
# See the "Running on macOS" section of README.md.
factory/data/**          text eol=lf
strategies/gen_*.py      text eol=lf
configs/wfo/gen_*.yaml   text eol=lf
